sequenceDiagram
    participant SupervisorAI
    participant Agent
    participant ReflectionEngine
    participant SelfImprovementEngine
    participant ContextManager

    Agent->>SupervisorAI: Task Result (Output, Status)
    SupervisorAI->>ReflectionEngine: Request Reflection (Task Output, Objective, Acceptance Criteria)
    ReflectionEngine->>ReflectionEngine: Review Output
    ReflectionEngine->>ReflectionEngine: Compare against Objectives
    ReflectionEngine->>ReflectionEngine: Detect Contradictions, Hallucinations, Weak Reasoning
    ReflectionEngine-->>SupervisorAI: Reflection Score & Recommendations

    alt If Reflection Score < Threshold
        SupervisorAI->>SelfImprovementEngine: Trigger Improvement (Agent, Recommendations)
        SelfImprovementEngine->>SelfImprovementEngine: Analyze Recommendations
        SelfImprovementEngine->>Agent: Update Agent Configuration/Strategy
        SelfImprovementEngine->>SupervisorAI: Improvement Applied
        SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Trigger Re-execution or Re-planning
    else Reflection Score >= Threshold
        SupervisorAI->>SupervisorAI: Mark Task as Complete/Accepted
    end

    ReflectionEngine->>ContextManager: Record Reflection History
    ContextManager-->>ReflectionEngine: Confirmation
